line_1: The mountain top with usual dulness kiss'd,
line_2: Fresh as the morning, which, enrob'd in mist,

line_1: A thousand times her Eyes I kiss'd,
line_2: Ten thousand more her snowy Breast;

line_1: Drank to their sons, their wives, their daughters kiss'd;
line_2: His lordship took each ploughman by the fist,
